  "author": "MintFace",
  "excerpt": "The pioneers of cryptoart in New Zealand peeled away from the norms of waiting to be picked by a gallery and created their own opportunities. These are the collective that began it all and never stopped believing.",
  "categories": [
    "Artist Features",
    "New Zealand",
    "News On The Line"
